{"_path":"/maps/_person/technology/peter-steinberger","_dir":"technology","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"","title":"Peter Steinberger","description":"PSPDFKit 创始人、Claudebot 创建者，Agentic Engineering 倡导者","original_path":"content/6.maps/_person/peter-steinberger.md","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"简介"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"简介？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Peter Steinberger 是奥地利资深开发者，PSPDFKit（PDF 框架，用于超 10 亿设备）的创始人。2024 年离开 PSPDFKit 后，创建了 Claudebot——一个开源的个人 AI 助手项目，短期内迅速获得社区关注（GitHub 3k+ stars）。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"主要贡献观点"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"主要贡献/观点？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Agentic Engineering 方法论"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"区分于随意的 \"vibe coding\"，提出有意识、架构驱动的 AI 协作方式："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"单日可合并 600+ commits，秘诀是并行运行 5-10 个 agents"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"与 AI \"讨论\"而非直接下指令，让它探索多种方案后再决定"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"自己不写代码，但深度把控架构方向"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Closing the Loop 原则"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"AI 擅长编码的核心原因是代码可被验证。设计\"可验证的架构\"让 AI 能自我测试、自我调试，本地测试比 CI 更快。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"从 PR 到 Prompt Request"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"将 GitHub PR 重新定义为 \"Prompt Request\"——重要的不是代码是什么，而是如何得到这段代码的思考过程。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"对 MCP 的批判"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"认为 MCP 是\"临时拐杖\"，CLI 更灵活：可以用 "},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":[]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"jq"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 精确过滤、管道组合、按需调用，而非预加载所有函数定义污染上下文。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"企业 AI 采用障碍"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"现有公司很难高效采用 AI，因为需要重构整个组织和代码库，优化代码库是为了让 agent 易于理解，而非人类工程师的偏好。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/the-pragmatic-engineer/id1457313865","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"The Pragmatic Engineer Podcast 访谈"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://github.com/steipete/claudebot","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Claudebot GitHub"}]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:6.maps:_person:technology:peter-steinberger.md","_source":"content","_file":"6.maps/_person/technology/peter-steinberger.md","_stem":"6.maps/_person/technology/peter-steinberger","_extension":"md"}